  "prompt": "What is the AT&T wireless voicemail number?",
  "response": "To access your AT&T wireless voicemail, you typically can dial **1** on your AT&T mobile phone. Alternatively, you can access your voicemail by holding the number **1** on your keypad or by dialing your own phone number. If you need to access voicemail from a different phone, you can call your mobile number and follow the prompts to check your voicemail. \n\nFor specific instructions or updates, it's always best to refer to the AT&T website or customer service.",
